#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Configuration Dialog</interface> contains all the options for "
"changing some of the default behaviour of &appname;."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</interface> vsebuje vse možnosti "
"za spreminjanje nekaterih privzetih lastnosti &appname;."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button <action>causes the changes "
"to take effect immediately</action> without closing the dialog, while "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> <action>applies the changes and closes the dialog</"
"action>. <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> closes the dialog, but any changes "
"already made and applied will remain. The <guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> "
"button <action>reverts the options</action> on the current page of the "
"dialog to their default values, while <guibutton>Help</guibutton> "
"<action>opens the &khelpcenter;</action> to the relative section of the "
"&appname; manual."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete gumb <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton> <action>povzroči, da "
"spremembe začnejo veljati takoj</action>, ne da bi zaprli pogovorno okno, "
"medtem ko <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> <action>uveljavi spremembe in zapre "
"pogovorno okno</action>. <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton> zapre pogovorno "
"okno, vendar bodo vse že narejene in uporabljene spremembe ostale. Gumb "
"<guibutton>Privzete</guibutton> <action>povrne možnosti</action> na trenutni "
"strani pogovornega okna na njihove privzete vrednosti, medtem ko "
"<guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton> <action>odpre &khelpcenter;</action> v "
"relativnem odseku priročnika &appname;."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some minor settings can only be changed by editing the configuration file "
"itself. See <link linkend=\"hidden-options\">Hidden Options</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere manjše nastavitve je mogoče spremeniti samo z urejanjem same "
"konfiguracijske datoteke. Glejte <link linkend=\"hidden-options\">Skrite "
"možnosti</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuration.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Options"
msgstr "Splošne možnosti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configuration.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "The General Options Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno s splošnimi možnostmi"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>General Options</guilabel> control the general behavior. "
"Images may be saved in the data file itself, saved separately in the common "
"&appname; application folder, or saved to a directory with the same name as "
"the data file, with <emphasis>_files</emphasis> appended to the name. For "
"collections with many images, saving them in the data file is much slower to "
"use. When &appname; is started, it can automatically reopen the last data "
"file that was open. The <interface>Quick Filter</interface> in the toolbar "
"is useful for easily filtering through your collection and can utilize "
"regular expressions."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Splošne možnosti</guilabel> nadzorujejo splošno vedenje. Slike se "
"lahko shranijo v samo podatkovno datoteko, shranjene ločeno v skupno "
"&appname; aplikacijsko mapo ali shranjene v imenik z enakim imenom kot "
"podatkovna datoteka, z dodanim <emphasis>_files</emphasis> k imenu. Pri "
"zbirkah z veliko slikami je njihovo shranjevanje v podatkovno datoteko "
"veliko počasnejše. Ko se  &appname; zažene, lahko samodejno znova odpre "
"zadnjo odprto podatkovno datoteko. <interface>Hitri filter</interface> v "
"orodni vrstici je uporaben za enostavno filtriranje vaše zbirke in lahko "
"uporablja regularne izraze."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Formatting Options</guilabel> control the level of automatic "
"formatting that &appname; does. For examples, see the <link linkend=\"field-"
"formatting\">Field Formatting section</link>. Capitalization and formatting "
"are distinct options, since a field may be capitalized without having the "
"order of the words changed, and vice-versa. The auto-capitalization can be "
"changed to ignore certain words. The automatic formatting includes "
"grammatical articles in titles, along with prefixes and suffixes for "
"personal names. The values are case-insensitive, and should be separated by "
"a semi-colon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Možnosti oblikovanja</guilabel> nadzirajo raven samodejnega "
"oblikovanja, ki ga izvede &appname;. Za primere si oglejte <link linkend="
"\"field-formatting\">razdelek o oblikovanju polj</link>. Uporaba velikih "
"začetnic in oblikovanje sta različni možnosti, saj lahko polje napišete z "
"velikimi črkami, ne da bi spremenili vrstni red besed, in obratno. Samodejno "
"uporabo velikih začetnic je mogoče spremeniti tako, da prezre določene "
"besede. Samodejno oblikovanje vključuje slovnične člene v naslovih, skupaj s "
"predponami in priponami za osebna imena. Vrednosti se ne razlikujejo med "
"velikimi in malimi črkami, zato morajo biti ločene s podpičjem."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The formatting rules follow general English usage, which may not work for "
"other languages. Articles are appended to the end of the title, with a "
"comma. Personal names are formatted to have the last name first, followed by "
"a comma, then the first name. Personal suffixes, such as Jr., are kept with "
"the last name. Prefixes, such as <emphasis>von</emphasis>, are kept with the "
"last name, but are ignored when the values are being sorted."
msgstr ""
"Pravila oblikovanja sledijo splošni angleški rabi, ki morda ne bo delovala "
"za druge jezike. Členi se dodajajo na koncu naslova, z vejico. Osebna imena "
"so oblikovana tako, da je najprej priimek, nato vejica in nato ime. Ob "
"priimku se ohranijo osebne pripone, kot je ml. Predpone, kot je "
"<emphasis>von</emphasis>, se ohranijo pri priimku, vendar se pri razvrščanju "
"vrednosti ne upoštevajo."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>John Q. von Public, III</emphasis> would become <emphasis>von "
"Public, III, John Q.</emphasis> and <emphasis>Public</emphasis> would be "
"used as the sort key."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>John Q. von Public, III</emphasis> bi postal <emphasis>von Public, "
"III, John Q.</emphasis> in <emphasis>Public</emphasis> bi bil uporabljen kot "
"ključ za razvrščanje."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only single word prefixes are supported. If a name includes <emphasis>van "
"der</emphasis>, for example, both <emphasis>van</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis>der</emphasis> should be included in the surname prefix list. "
"Articles ending with an apostrophe are supported for sorting order, as well."
msgstr ""
"Podprte so samo predpone ene same besede. Če ime vključuje na primer "
"<emphasis>van der</emphasis>, morata biti tako <emphasis>van</emphasis> kot "
"<emphasis>der</emphasis> vključena na seznam predpon priimkov. Članki, ki se "
"končajo z apostrofom, so podprti tudi za vrstni red razvrščanja."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actual values in the collection are <emphasis>not</emphasis> changed, "
"only the visible text used for the interface. So the formatting options can "
"be changed back and forth without affecting any of the data in the "
"collection."
msgstr ""
"Dejanske vrednosti v zbirki <emphasis>niso</emphasis> spremenjene, samo "
"vidno besedilo, uporabljeno za vmesnik. Tako je mogoče možnosti oblikovanja "
"spreminjati naprej in nazaj, ne da bi to vplivalo na podatke v zbirki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuration.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing Options"
msgstr "Možnosti tiskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; uses an &xslt; template for creating &HTML; and then passes that "
"to the &kde; printing service. Only the fields visible in the <link linkend="
"\"detailed-view\"><interface>Column View</interface></link> are printed. "
"Furthermore, if the collection is being filtered, only the visible entries "
"will be printed. Initially, a warning message is shown if filtering is "
"active."
msgstr ""
"&appname; uporablja predlogo &xslt; za ustvarjanje &HTML; in nato to "
"posreduje datoteki &kde; za storitev tiskanja. Natisnjena so samo polja, ki "
"so vidna v <link linkend=\"detailed-view\"><interface>pogledu stolpcev</"
"interface></link>. Poleg tega, če je zbirka filtrirana, bodo natisnjeni samo "
"vidni vnosi. Na začetku se prikaže opozorilo, če je filtriranje aktivno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configuration.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Print Options Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno možnosti tiskanja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configuration.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Print Options Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno možnosti tiskanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Printing Options</guilabel> allow you to change some "
"formatting when printing a collection. If <guilabel>Format titles and names</"
"guilabel> is checked, then the fields are <link linkend=\"field-formatting"
"\">auto-formatted</link> when they are printed. Otherwise, they are printed "
"exactly as they were entered."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Možnosti tiskanja</guilabel> vam omogočajo, da spremenite nekaj "
"oblikovanja pri tiskanju zbirke. Če je označeno <guilabel>Oblikuj naslove in "
"imena</guilabel>, so polja <link linkend=\"field-formatting\">samodejno "
"oblikovana</link>, ko so natisnjena. V nasprotnem primeru se natisnejo točno "
"tako, kot so bili vneseni."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default printing stylesheet prints the collection with the field values "
"in columns. <guilabel>Print field headers</guilabel> controls whether the "
"field title is printed at the top of the column."
msgstr ""
"Privzet seznam slogov za tiskanje natisne zbirko z vrednostmi polj v "
"stolpcih. <guilabel>Natisni glave polj</guilabel> nadzira, ali je naslov "
"polja natisnjen na vrhu stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the printout, the entries will be sorted as they are in the <link linkend="
"\"detailed-view\"><interface>Column View</interface></link>. Additionally, "
"they may be grouped as they are in the <link linkend=\"group-view"
"\"><interface>Group View</interface></link>."
msgstr ""
"V izpisu bodo vnosi razvrščeni tako, kot so v <link linkend=\"detailed-view"
"\"><interface>pogledu stolpcev</interface></link>. Poleg tega so lahko "
"združeni, kot so, v <link linkend=\"group-view\"><interface>pogledu skupine</"
"interface></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, when image fields are included in the printout, the images may be "
"resized, while maintaining their aspect ratio. The maximum image width and "
"height define the largest possible size of the image, though it will never "
"be increased."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje, ko so slikovna polja vključena v izpis, se lahko slikam spremeni "
"velikost, pri čemer se ohrani njihovo razmerje stranic. Največja širina in "
"višina slike določata največjo možno velikost slike, ki pa se nikoli ne "
"poveča."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuration.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Template Options"
msgstr "Možnosti predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"entry-view\"><interface>Entry View</interface></link> "
"uses templates to show the field values. You can specify a different "
"template for each collection type. Some templates, such as the "
"<emphasis>Album</emphasis> or <emphasis>Video</emphasis> templates are for a "
"specific collection type, and a short error message will appear in the "
"<interface>Entry View</interface> if they are used for other types. The "
"<guilabel>Preview</guilabel> button pops up a window to show you a preview "
"of what the template looks like. Custom fonts and colors may be passed to "
"the template, and all of the default templates will honor those settings. "
"However, custom template may choose to ignore them."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"entry-view\"><interface>Pogled vnosa</interface></link> "
"uporablja predloge za prikaz vrednosti polj. Za vsako vrsto zbirke lahko "
"določite drugo predlogo. Nekatere predloge, kot so predloge <emphasis>Album</"
"emphasis> ali <emphasis>Video</emphasis>, so za določeno vrsto zbirke in v "
"<interface>Pogledu vnosa</interface> se prikaže kratko sporočilo o napaki, "
"če uporabljajo se za druge vrste. Gumb <guilabel>Predogled</guilabel> odpre "
"okno, ki vam pokaže predogled, kako je videti predloga. Pisave in barve po "
"meri se lahko posredujejo predlogi in vse privzete predloge bodo upoštevale "
"te nastavitve. Predloga po meri pa jih lahko prezre."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional templates may be installed directly, or downloaded from <ulink "
"url=\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink> by clicking the "
"<guilabel>Download</guilabel> button. Any templates installed by the user "
"may also be deleted. Entry templates are saved in <filename class=\"directory"
"\">~/.local/share/tellico/entry-templates/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne predloge lahko namestite neposredno ali jih prenesete s <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink> s klikom na gumb "
"<guilabel>Prenesi</guilabel>. Vse predloge, ki jih je namestil uporabnik, se "
"lahko tudi izbrišejo. Vnosne predloge so shranjene v <filename class="
"\"directory\">~/.local/share/tellico/entry-templates/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create a new template, please consider submitting it at <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>!"
msgstr ""
"Če ustvarite novo predlogo, razmislite o predložitvi na <ulink url=\"https://"
"store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configuration.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Template Options Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno možnosti predloge</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configuration.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Template Options Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno možnosti predloge</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuration.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Sources Options"
msgstr "Možnosti podatkovnih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; can use various sources for importing data, which can be "
"configured in the Data Sources Dialog. There are many available types and "
"sources. A few of them are listed below, while the full list is <ulink url="
"\"https://tellico-project.org/data-sources\">available on the Tellico web "
"site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&appname; lahko uporablja različne vire za uvoz podatkov, ki jih je mogoče "
"konfigurirati v pogovornem oknu Viri podatkov. Na voljo je veliko vrst in "
"virov. Nekaj jih je navedenih spodaj, celoten seznam pa je <ulink url="
"\"https://tellico-project.org/data-sources\">na voljo na spletnem mestu "
"Tellico</ulink>."

