#. Tag: screeninfo
#: configuration.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Data Sources Options Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno z možnostmi virov podatkov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configuration.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Data Sources Options Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno možnosti virov podatkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New sources may be added by clicking the <guibutton>New...</guibutton> "
"button, while existing ones may be modified or deleted, using the "
"<guibutton>Modify...</guibutton> or <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> buttons. "
"The order of the sources, which shows up in the entry updating menus, can "
"also be changed."
msgstr ""
"Nove vire lahko dodate s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Novo ...</guibutton>, "
"obstoječe pa lahko spremenite ali izbrišete z uporabo gumbov "
"<guibutton>Spremeni...</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton>. "
"Vrstni red virov, ki se prikaže v menijih za posodabljanje vnosov, je mogoče "
"tudi spremeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many of the data sources offer more information than the default fields in "
"&appname;. Those other fields are shown on the right of the configuration "
"box. If any of those fields are checked, they will be added to the "
"collection when an entry is added from that source."
msgstr ""
"Številni viri podatkov ponujajo več informacij kot privzeta polja v "
"&appname;. Ta druga polja so prikazana na desni strani konfiguracijskega "
"polja. Če je katero koli od teh polj označeno, bo dodano v zbirko, ko bo "
"dodan vnos iz tega vira."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Book and Bibliographic Data Sources"
msgstr "Knjižni in bibliografski viri podatkov"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "z39.50 Servers"
msgstr "z39.50 Strežniki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <ulink url=\"http://www.cni.org/pub/NISO/docs/Z39.50-brochure/50."
"brochure.toc.html\">z39.50 protocol</ulink> is used to access libraries and "
"bibliographic information providers around the world. Lists of public z39.50 "
"servers are <ulink url=\"http://www.indexdata.dk/targettest/\">available "
"from indexdata.dk</ulink>, among others. &appname; comes with several preset "
"configurations for major libraries, or you can specify the connection "
"information manually."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do knjižnic se uporablja <ulink url=\"http://www.cni.org/pub/NISO/"
"docs/Z39.50-brochure/50.brochure.toc.html\">protokol z39.50</ulink> in "
"ponudniki bibliografskih informacij po vsem svetu. Seznami javnih strežnikov "
"z39.50 so med drugim <ulink url=\"http://www.indexdata.dk/targettest/\">na "
"voljo na indexdata.dk</ulink>. &appname; prihaja z več prednastavljenimi "
"konfiguracijami za glavne knjižnice ali pa lahko informacije o povezavi "
"določite ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; is able to read data in the <acronym>MODS</acronym>, "
"<acronym>USMARC</acronym>/<acronym>MARC21</acronym>, or <acronym>UNIMARC</"
"acronym> format, using the <ulink url=\"http://www.indexdata.dk/yaz/\">yaz "
"library</ulink>. In addition, there is limited support for the "
"<acronym>GRS-1</acronym> format."
msgstr ""
"&appname; lahko bere podatke v formatu <acronym>MODS</acronym>, "
"<acronym>USMARC</acronym>/<acronym>MARC21</acronym> ali <acronym>UNIMARC</"
"acronym> z uporabo <ulink url =\"http://www.indexdata.dk/yaz/\">knjižnica "
"yaz</ulink>. Poleg tega obstaja omejena podpora za format <acronym>GRS-1</"
"acronym>."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use one of the preset libraries, check the box and then select the "
"library. The other configuration entries will be disabled. If you need to "
"set the information manually, uncheck the preset box."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti eno od prednastavljenih knjižnic, potrdite polje in nato "
"izberite knjižnico. Drugi konfiguracijski vnosi bodo onemogočeni. Če morate "
"podatke nastaviti ročno, počistite polje prednastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default port for z39.50 access is 210, but some servers may use a "
"different one. &appname; assumes the server uses the MARC-8 character "
"encoding, unless configured otherwise. If an incorrect character encoding is "
"used, an error message may appear on the program output, or possibly no "
"entries are retrieved."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta vrata za dostop z39.50 so 210, vendar nekateri strežniki morda "
"uporabljajo drugačna. &appname; predvideva, da strežnik uporablja kodiranje "
"znakov MARC-8, razen če je konfigurirano drugače. Če je uporabljeno "
"nepravilno kodiranje znakov, se lahko na izhodu programa prikaže sporočilo o "
"napaki ali pa se vnosi ne pridobijo."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some servers require a username and password for access. &appname; can use "
"and save that password, but be aware that is written to the &appname; "
"configuration file in plain text and is not secure. For most public servers, "
"the username and password fields may be left empty."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri strežniki za dostop zahtevajo uporabniško ime in geslo. &appname; "
"lahko uporabi in shrani to geslo, vendar se zavedajte, da je zapisano v "
"&appname; konfiguracijsko datoteko v navadnem besedilu in ni varno. Za "
"večino javnih strežnikov lahko polji za uporabniško ime in geslo ostaneta "
"prazni."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "SRU Servers"
msgstr "SRU strežniki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>SRU</acronym> stands for <ulink url=\"http://www.loc.gov/standards/"
"sru/\">Search/Retrieve via &URL;</ulink> and is a standard search protocol "
"for Internet searches. Some libraries use it for providing access to their "
"data catalogs. Among them, the <ulink url=\"http://www.loc.gov/z3950/"
"lcserver.html#oppr\">US Library of Congress</ulink> is probably the best "
"known."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>SRU</acronym> pomeni <ulink url=\"http://www.loc.gov/standards/sru/"
"\">Search/Retrieve via &URL;</ulink> in je standardni iskalni protokol za "
"internetna iskanja. Nekatere knjižnice ga uporabljajo za zagotavljanje "
"dostopa do svojih podatkovnih katalogov. Med njimi je verjetno najbolj znana "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.loc.gov/z3950/lcserver.html#oppr\">Kongresna "
"knjižnica ZDA</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Custom fields can be added to tweak Tellico's interaction with the SRU "
"server. To override particular query protocols, use the x-tellico prefix and "
"the desired field name. For example, to query ISBN using the bib schema "
"instead of the bath schema, set <userinput>x-tellico-isbn</"
"userinput>=<userinput>bib.isbn</userinput>. &tellico; can also make the SRU "
"request by the POST method, if <userinput>x-tellico-method</"
"userinput>=<userinput>POST</userinput>. In order to override the record "
"schema, add a custom field setting <userinput>recordSchema</"
"userinput>=<userinput>unimarcXchange</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Polja po meri je mogoče dodati za prilagoditev interakcije Tellica s "
"strežnikom SRU. Za preglasitev določenih protokolov poizvedb uporabite "
"predpono x-tellico in želeno ime polja. Na primer, za poizvedbo po ISBN z "
"uporabo sheme bib namesto sheme bath nastavite <userinput>x-tellico-isbn</"
"userinput>=<userinput>bib.isbn</userinput>. &tellico; lahko zahtevo SRU "
"izvede tudi z metodo POST, če je <userinput>x-tellico-method</"
"userinput>=<userinput>POST</userinput>. Če želite preglasiti shemo zapisa, "
"dodajte nastavitev polja po meri <userinput>recordSchema</"
"userinput>=<userinput>unimarcXchange</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entrez Databases"
msgstr "Podatkovne baze Entrez"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/Entrez/\">Entrez</ulink> is the "
"integrated, text-based search and retrieval system used at the National "
"Center for Biotechnology Information (NCBI). The most well-known Entrez "
"database is <ulink url=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?"
"db=PubMed\">PubMed</ulink>, the database for life science articles from many "
"biological journals. At the moment, the only Entrez database supported by "
"&appname; is PubMed."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/Entrez/\">Entrez</ulink> je "
"integriran sistem iskanja in pridobivanja, ki temelji na besedilu in se "
"uporablja v Nacionalnem centru za biotehnološke informacije (NCBI). . "
"Najbolj znana zbirka podatkov Entrez je <ulink url=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih."
"gov/entrez/query.fcgi?db=PubMed\">PubMed</ulink>, baza podatkov za članke o "
"znanosti o življenju iz številnih bioloških revij. Trenutno je edina zbirka "
"podatkov Entrez, ki jo podpira &appname; je PubMed."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bibliographic Databases"
msgstr "Bibliografske baze podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://arxiv.org\">arXiv.org</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://"
"bibsonomy.org\">Bibsonomy</ulink>, and <ulink url=\"http://crossref.org"
"\">CrossRef</ulink> are online databases for academic articles and "
"bibliographic information. For access to the CrossRef source, you must "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.crossref.org/requestaccount/\">request an account</"
"ulink> and add your account information to the data source configuration."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://arxiv.org\">arXiv.org</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://"
"bibsonomy.org\">Bibsonomy</ulink> in <ulink url=\"http: //crossref.org"
"\">CrossRef</ulink> so spletne zbirke podatkov za akademske članke in "
"bibliografske informacije. Za dostop do vira CrossRef morate <ulink url="
"\"http://www.crossref.org/requestaccount/\">zahtevati račun</ulink> in "
"dodati podatke o računu v konfiguracijo vira podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISBNdb.com"
msgstr "ISBNdb.com"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://isbndb.com\">ISBNdb.com</ulink> is an online book "
"database, from libraries around the world."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://isbndb.com\">ISBNdb.com</ulink> je spletna zbirka "
"podatkov o knjigah iz knjižnic po vsem svetu."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenLibrary.org"
msgstr "OpenLibrary.org"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://openlibrary.org\">OpenLibrary.org</ulink> is an online "
"book database that aims to have one page for every book."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://openlibrary.org\">OpenLibrary.org</ulink> je spletna "
"zbirka podatkov o knjigah, katere namen je imeti eno stran za vsako knjigo."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "OPDS Catalogs"
msgstr "OPDS katalogi"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Open_Publication_Distribution_System\">OPDS catalogs</ulink> provide a means "
"for searching (and distributing) digital books. &tellico; can use many OPDS "
"catalogs as a data source, such as <ulink url=\"https://wiki.mobileread.com/"
"wiki/OPDS\">Project Gutenberg</ulink>. Enter the link to the catalog and "
"verify the access and format to confirm &tellico; can read the link."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Open_Publication_Distribution_System\">Katalogi OPDS</ulink> zagotavljajo "
"sredstva za iskanje (in distribucijo) digitalnih knjig. &tellico; lahko kot "
"vir podatkov uporabi številne kataloge OPDS, kot je <ulink url=\"https://"
"wiki.mobileread.com/wiki/OPDS\">Projekt Gutenberg</ulink>. Vnesite povezavo "
"do kataloga in preverite dostop in format za potrditev &tellico; lahko "
"preberete povezavo."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comic Book Data Sources"
msgstr "Viri podatkov o stripih"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bedetheque"
msgstr "Bedetheque"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.bedetheque.com\">Bedetheque</ulink> is a French "
"comic book database, managed by BDGest."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.bedetheque.com\">Bedetheque</ulink> je francoska "
"zbirka podatkov o stripih, ki jo upravlja BDGest."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comic Vine"
msgstr "Comic Vine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/\">Comic Vine</ulink> is billed "
"as the largest comic book wiki in the universe."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/\">Comic Vine</ulink> velja za "
"največji stripovski wiki v vesolju."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Movie Data Sources"
msgstr "Viri filmskih podatkov"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Internet Movie Database"
msgstr "Internetna zbirka podatkov o filmih"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <ulink url=\"http://www.imdb.com\">Internet Movie Database</ulink> "
"provides information about movies and videos. When a search is conducted for "
"a <emphasis>Person</emphasis>, if more than one possible result is returned, "
"a dialog box is opened to allow you to select the correct person. The "
"configuration options include selecting which IMDb nationality to use and "
"whether images are fetched or not. Since IMDb can return a large number of "
"cast members, you can limit that to a certain number."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.imdb.com\">Internet Movie Database</ulink> nudi "
"informacije o filmih in videih. Če se pri iskanju <emphasis>osebe</emphasis> "
"vrne več kot en možni rezultat, se odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko "
"izberete pravo osebo. Možnosti konfiguracije vključujejo izbiro, katero "
"državo IMDb želite uporabiti in ali so slike pridobljene ali ne. Ker lahko "
"IMDb vrne veliko število članov zasedbe, lahko to omejite na določeno "
"število."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "TheMovieDB.org"
msgstr "TheMovieDB.org"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://themoviedb.org\">TheMovieDB.org</ulink> is a free and "
"open online movie database. Registration for a free account is required."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://themoviedb.org\">TheMovieDB.org</ulink> je prosta in "
"odprta spletna zbirka podatkov o filmih. Za brezplačen račun je potrebna "
"registracija."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Open Movie Database"
msgstr "Open Movie Database"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://omdbapi.com\">The Open Movie Database (OMDBAPI.com)</"
"ulink> is a free web service to obtain movie information."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://omdbapi.com\">Open Movie Database (OMDBAPI.com)</ulink> "
"je brezplačna spletna storitev za pridobivanje informacij o filmih."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "FilmAffinity"
msgstr "FilmAffinity"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://filmaffinity.com\">FilmAffinity</ulink> is an "
"independent film site."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://filmaffinity.com\">FilmAffinity</ulink> je neodvisna "
"filmska stran."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Music Data Sources"
msgstr "Glasbeni podatkovni viri"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Discogs.com"
msgstr "Discogs.com"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://discogs.com\">Discogs.com</ulink> is a user-built music "
"database containing information on artists, labels, and their recordings. "
"Registration for a free account is required."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://discogs.com\">Discogs.com</ulink> je glasbena baza "
"podatkov, ki jo ustvarijo uporabniki in vsebuje informacije o izvajalcih, "
"založbah in njihovih posnetkih. Za brezplačen račun je potrebna registracija."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "MusicBrainz.org"
msgstr "MusicBrainz.org"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://musicbrainz.org\">MusicBrainz.org</ulink> is a community "
"music metadatabase that attempts to create a comprehensive music information "
"site."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://musicbrainz.org\">MusicBrainz.org</ulink> je zbirka "
"glasbenih metapodatkov skupnosti, ki poskuša ustvariti obsežno spletno mesto "
"z glasbenimi informacijami."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "iTunes Search"
msgstr "iskanje iTunes"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <ulink url=\"https://performance-partners.apple.com/search-api\">iTunes "
"Search</ulink> provides information on content within the iTunes Store and "
"Apple Books Store. You can search for a variety of content; including books, "
"movies, podcasts, music, music videos, audiobooks, and TV shows."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://performance-partners.apple.com/search-api\">iTunes "
"Search</ulink> ponuja informacije o vsebini v trgovinah iTunes Store in "
"Apple Books Store. Iščete lahko različne vsebine, vključno s knjigami, "
"filmi, podcasti, glasbo, glasbenimi videoposnetki, zvočnimi knjigami in TV-"
"oddajami."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Video Game Data Sources"
msgstr "Viri podatkov o video igrah"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "GiantBomb.com"
msgstr "GiantBomb.com"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://giantbomb.com\">GiantBomb.com</ulink> is a large "
"community-driven video game database. Registration for a free account is "
"required."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://giantbomb.com\">GiantBomb.com</ulink> je velika zbirka "
"podatkov o video igrah, ki jo vodi skupnost. Za brezplačen račun je potrebna "
"registracija."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "TheGamesDB.net"
msgstr "TheGamesDB.net"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://thegamesdb.net\">TheGamesDB.net</ulink> is an open, "
"online database for video game fans."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://thegamesdb.net\">TheGamesDB.net</ulink> je odprta "
"spletna zbirka podatkov za ljubitelje video iger."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "MobyGames"
msgstr "MobyGames"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://www.mobygames.com\">MobyGames.com</ulink> is self-"
"described as the oldest, largest and most accurate video game database."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://www.mobygames.com\">MobyGames.com</ulink> se sam "
"opisuje kot najstarejša, največja in najbolj natančna zbirka podatkov o "
"video igrah."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "IGDB.com"
msgstr "IGDB.com"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://www.igdb.com\">IGDB.com</ulink> calls itself a gaming "
"website for everyone that loves game."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://www.igdb.com\">IGDB.com</ulink> se imenuje spletno "
"mesto za igre za vse, ki imajo radi igre."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "VideoGameGeek"
msgstr "VideoGameGeek"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://videogamegeek.com\">VideoGameGeek</ulink> is an online "
"video gaming resource and community."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://videogamegeek.com\">VideoGameGeek</ulink> je spletni "
"vir in skupnost video iger."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Board Game Data Sources"
msgstr "Viri podatkov o družabnih igrah"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "BoardGameGeek"
msgstr "BoardGameGeek"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://boardgamegeek.com\">BoardGameGeek</ulink> is an online "
"board gaming resource and community."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://boardgamegeek.com\">BoardGameGeek</ulink> je spletni "
"vir in skupnost za družabne igre."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coin &amp; Stamp Data Sources"
msgstr "Kovanec &amp; Viri podatkov o znamkah"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colnect"
msgstr "Colnect"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://colnect.com\">Colnect</ulink> is an online community "
"for collectibles providing personal collection management. &tellico; can "
"search Colnect for coin and stamp information, as well as comic books, "
"sports card, and video games."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://colnect.com\">Colnect</ulink> je spletna skupnost "
"zbirateljskih predmetov, ki omogoča upravljanje osebnih zbirk. &tellico; "
"lahko v Colnectu išče informacije o kovancih in znamkah, pa tudi stripe, "
"športne kartice in video igre."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numista"
msgstr "Numista"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://numista.com\">Numista</ulink> is a world coin catalog "
"which grows thanks to member contributions, offering online collection "
"management, tools to easily exchange with other collectors, and a forum."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://numista.com\">Numista</ulink> je svetovni katalog "
"kovancev, ki raste zahvaljujoč prispevkom članov, ponuja spletno upravljanje "
"zbirk, orodja za preprosto izmenjavo z drugimi zbiralci in forum."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Sources for Multiple Collection Types"
msgstr "Viri podatkov za več vrst zbirk"

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amazon.com"
msgstr "Amazon.com"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the Amazon Web Services, &appname; can search any of 14 different "
"international sites operated by <ulink url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon.com</"
"ulink> for information: United States, United Kingdom, Germany, Japan, "
"France, Canada, China, Spain, Italy, Brazil, Australia, India, Mexico, and "
"Turkey."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba spletnih storitev Amazon, &appname; lahko išče informacije na "
"katerem koli od 14 različnih mednarodnih spletnih mest, ki jih upravlja "
"<ulink url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon.com</ulink>: Združene države, "
"Združeno kraljestvo, Nemčija, Japonska, Francija, Kanada, Kitajska, Španija, "
"Italija, Brazilija, Avstralija, Indija, Mehika in Turčija."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuring each Amazon.com source involves three settings: the server "
"location, image size, and associate's ID. Some information from <ulink url="
"\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon.com</ulink> may include an image, such as a "
"book or video cover. That image may be downloaded in three different sizes, "
"depending on the item. The associate's ID must be used to access the Amazon."
"com Web Services, and is included in the links back to the item, as dictated "
"by the license agreement for the use of the Amazon.com Web Services."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguriranje vsakega vira Amazon.com vključuje tri nastavitve: lokacijo "
"strežnika, velikost slike in ID sodelavca. Nekatere informacije iz <ulink "
"url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon.com</ulink> lahko vključujejo sliko, na "
"primer naslovnico knjige ali videa. To sliko je mogoče prenesti v treh "
"različnih velikostih, odvisno od predmeta. ID sodelavca je treba uporabiti "
"za dostop do spletnih storitev Amazon.com in je vključen v povratne povezave "
"do artikla, kot narekuje licenčna pogodba za uporabo spletnih storitev "
"Amazon.com."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Access to the <ulink url=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSECommerceService/"
"latest/DG/Welcome.html\">Amazon Product Advertising API</ulink> may have "
"restrictions related to sales referrals or advertising. Refer to the Amazon "
"documentation for further information when signing up for API access."
msgstr ""
"Dostop do <ulink url=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSECommerceService/"
"latest/DG/Welcome.html\">API-ja za oglaševanje izdelkov Amazon</ulink> ima "
"lahko omejitve, povezane s priporočili za prodajo ali oglaševanjem. Za "
"dodatne informacije glejte dokumentacijo Amazona, ko se prijavljate za "
"dostop API."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "External Scripts or Applications"
msgstr "Zunanji skripti ali aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As an easier way for &appname; to integrate with third-party plugins, "
"external scripts or applications may be used as an interface for searching "
"other information sources. &appname; will execute a command, and pass the "
"search terms as command-line options."
msgstr ""
"Kot lažji način za &appname; za integracijo z vtičniki tretjih oseb se lahko "
"zunanji skripti ali aplikacije uporabljajo kot vmesnik za iskanje drugih "
"virov informacij. &appname; bo izvedel ukaz in posredoval iskalne izraze kot "
"možnosti ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some scripts are distributed with &appname; itself. <ulink url=\"http://"
"python.org\">Python</ulink> is required to search <ulink url=\"http://"
"darkhorse.com\">Dark Horse Comics</ulink>, a comic book publisher, for "
"example."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri skripti se distribuirajo z &appname; sama. <ulink url=\"http://"
"python.org\">Python</ulink> je potreben za iskanje <ulink url=\"http://"
"darkhorse.com\">Dark Horse Comics</ulink>, založnika stripov, na primer."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The collection type returned by the script must be set, along with the data "
"format. Not only can &appname; import data from scripts that use the <link "
"linkend=\"file-format\">default &appname; &XML; format</link>, but it can "
"also import other formats as well, such as bibtex."
msgstr ""
"Nastaviti je treba vrsto zbirke, ki jo vrne skript, skupaj z obliko "
"podatkov. Ne samo, da lahko &appname; uvozi podatke iz skriptov, ki "
"uporabljajo <link linkend=\"file-format\">privzeto &appname; &XML; format</"
"link>, vendar lahko uvozi tudi druge formate, kot je bibtex."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full path to the application should be entered in the source options. "
"Check the boxes next to the search keys supported by the application, and "
"enter the required command line options in the edit box. The search value "
"will be inserted where <userinput>%1</userinput> appears."
msgstr ""
"Celotno pot do aplikacije je treba vnesti v možnostih vira. Potrdite polja "
"zraven iskalnih ključev, ki jih podpira aplikacija, in v polje za urejanje "
"vnesite zahtevane možnosti ukazne vrstice. Iskana vrednost bo vstavljena "
"tam, kjer se prikaže <userinput>%1</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Never install and run a script from an untrusted source. They are executed "
"with the same permissions as the user, and as a result, could modify or "
"delete files or otherwise mess up your system."
msgstr ""
"Nikoli ne namestite in ne zaženite skripta iz vira, ki mu ne zaupate. "
"Izvajajo se z enakimi dovoljenji kot uporabnik in posledično lahko "
"spremenijo ali izbrišejo datoteke ali kako drugače zmedejo vaš sistem."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For updating entries already in the collection, the final check box and edit "
"box are used to determine the command-line options. The entry fields used to "
"find an update must be entered, in the same format as used for <link linkend="
"\"derived\">derived value</link> fields."
msgstr ""
"Za posodabljanje vnosov, ki so že v zbirki, se za določitev možnosti ukazne "
"vrstice uporabita zadnje potrditveno polje in polje za urejanje. Vnosna "
"polja, ki se uporabljajo za iskanje posodobitve, je treba vnesti v isti "
"obliki, kot se uporablja za polja <link linkend=\"derived\">izpeljane "
"vrednosti</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuration.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple Combined Data Sources"
msgstr "Več kombiniranih podatkovnih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combinations of up to eight existing data sources can be used as a single "
"source, where each search result from the first source is updated from the "
"subsequent sources. The collection type to be used must be set before adding "
"sources."
msgstr ""
"Kombinacije do osmih obstoječih podatkovnih virov se lahko uporabljajo kot "
"en sam vir, kjer se vsak rezultat iskanja iz prvega vira posodobi iz "
"naslednjih virov. Vrsto zbirke, ki bo uporabljena, je treba nastaviti pred "
"dodajanjem virov."

#. Tag: para
#: configuration.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only existing data sources can be used in combination. Only the search type "
"for the first source can be used in this source since the results come from "
"the first data source. For example, a UPCitemDb search may first be done, "
"with each result then updated from the TheMovieDB."
msgstr ""
"V kombinaciji je mogoče uporabiti samo obstoječe vire podatkov. V tem viru "
"je mogoče uporabiti samo vrsto iskanja za prvi vir, saj rezultati prihajajo "
"iz prvega vira podatkov. Na primer, najprej se lahko izvede iskanje "
"UPCitemDb, pri čemer se vsak rezultat nato posodobi iz TheMovieDB."

